data.description: Spectacular on Spacewalk!  As you step inside, you'll be immediately captivated by the abundance of natural light pouring in through skylights and a large bay window on the main level. The vaulted ceiling and wood floors throughout create an inviting atmosphere. The open-concept design boasts granite countertops, a bar area, and stainless steel appliances in the kitchen, complemented by white cabinets and a butcher block buffet/prep area.    Upstairs, you'll discover three generously sized bedrooms, including a jack and jill bathroom accessible from both the hallway and the master bedroom. Storage space abounds throughout the home. The garden-level basement features a spacious rec room with upgraded carpeting, a large bedroom, and a 3/4 bath with a fully tiled shower. The laundry room and additional storage ensure you have everything you need. Outside, a large backyard beckons for outdoor enjoyment. Plus, this home is conveniently located close to shopping, dining, recreational centers, Peterson Air Force Base, and Fort Carson, making it the ideal place to call home.
